###
# Test del endpoint de HTR Service
# Usar con la extensión REST Client de VS Code
###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8004
@token = Bearer your-token-here

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### Service Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

### Root Endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Content-Type: application/json

### Procesar imagen HTR (ejemplo básico)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/htr/procesar
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="documento.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_image.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="documento_id"

123
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="tipo_sacramento"

bautizo
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Obtener resultados de HTR
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/htr/resultados/123
Content-Type: application/json
